-- Migration 052: Synchronize German matrix metadata umlauts.
--
-- Migration 006-049 originally inserted German matrix metadata with ASCII
-- transliterations. The canonical migration files now use native German
-- umlauts and eszett, but already-applied databases need this forward
-- migration to update the persisted matrix labels and help text.
--
-- Generated from the canonical matrix metadata in migrations 006-049.
-- Updated rows: 281 groups, 1611 criteria, 721 options.

